    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there is \"support\" but it doesn't change the fact that he's gone. it feels like i'm just a ghost living in a house that belongs to someone else now. sometimes i just sit here staring at his chair and think... what is even the point of dragging this out if the person who made life worth living isn't here?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
