      "content": "it feels like i'm a burden to everyone i talk to. every time i try to explain it, it just sounds like i'm complaining about something that's already happened. people say \"it gets better\" but it doesn't feel like it ever will. honestly, sometimes it feels more like a mercy to just stop feeling this way. like, if i could just go where he is, maybe the heaviness would finally stop.",
